OL,3,GOPINIONCFalling audiences and fading
OL,4,CUSP: uncertain future for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FOfcom is expected to open its
OL,7,Fconsultation on proposed changes to
OL,8,FSTV's news service within the next
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FThe broadcaster is proposing ditching
OL,12,Fthe separate news service for the
OL,13,Fformer Grampian TV region.
OL,15,FThe move is being fiercely opposed by
OL,16,Fthe National Union of Journalists and
OL,17,Fhas been condemned by the leaders of
OL,18,Fall the major political parties in the
OL,19,FScottish parliament.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
