OL,3,GOPINIONCFalling audiences and fading
OL,4,CUSP: uncertain future for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe NUJ is currently balloting its
OL,7,Fmembers at STV on strike action.
OL,9,FIt has been suggested that a strike in
OL,10,Fthe week before Christmas is a
OL,11,Fpossibility.
OL,13,FRegardless of what Ofcom may allow,
OL,14,Fsome changes seem inevitable.
OL,16,FSTV says it does not need permission to
OL,17,Fsimply move the presentation of the
OL,18,F"Grampian" bulletins to Glasgow and
OL,19,Frecord them.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
