OL,3,GOPINIONCFalling audiences and fading
OL,4,CUSP: uncertain future for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FThere is no suggestion at present that
OL,7,FSTV is planning any on air changes
OL,8,Fahead of Ofcom's decision.
OL,10,FPres fans may sometimes look to STV
OL,11,Fwith a certain curiosity or even envy `
OL,12,Fthe Channel 3 service which isn't owned
OL,13,Fby ITV and which still has local
OL,14,Fbranding.
OL,16,FI have been watching STV closely over
OL,17,Fthe past few weeks and it is hard to
OL,18,Fsee how viewers will still benefit from
OL,19,Fthis arrangement if the planned changes
OL,20,Fto news go ahead.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
