OL,3,GOPINIONCFalling audiences and fading
OL,4,CUSP: uncertain future for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FThe only thing which can be said in
OL,7,FSTV's favour at present is that its
OL,8,Fnews provision goes beyond that offered
OL,9,Fin Wales and Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FUntil now, the idea of retaining a
OL,12,Fseparate service for the former
OL,13,FGrampian region was never in any doubt.
OL,15,FThere are also sub-opts for the
OL,16,FEdinburgh and Dundee areas. These are
OL,17,Fnot historic legacies ` they were
OL,18,Fintroduced around 20 years ago.
