OL,3,GOPINIONCFalling audiences and fading
OL,4,CUSP: uncertain future for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FSTV's proposal would mean the company
OL,7,Fwould be producing what would probably
OL,8,Fturn out to be an inferior imitation of
OL,9,FBBC Reporting Scotland. A national news
OL,10,Fservice without the BBC's array of
OL,11,Fspecialist and long-standing reporters
OL,12,Fand correspondents.
OL,14,FIt is notable that a greater proportion
OL,15,Fof STV's on air staff are at relatively
OL,16,Fearly stages in their careers.
OL,18,FMore widely, STV now produces little
OL,19,Flocal output other than the current
OL,20,Faffairs programme Scotland Tonight and
OL,21,Fmagazine show What's On Scotland.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
