OL,5,
OL,6,FIf STV were bought over, say by ITV or
OL,7,FComcast, the legal obligation to
OL,8,Fproduce this minimum volume of output
OL,9,Fwould stay.
OL,11,FAs for junctions and promotions, they
OL,12,Flack ITV's polish.
OL,14,FThe idents haven't changed for 10
OL,15,Fyears.
