OL,4,CUSP: uncertain future for STV
OL,5,
OL,6,FSome promotional airtime is lost to
OL,7,Fsponsorship stings for the station
OL,8,Fitself ` a way of allowing extra
OL,9,Fadvertising within the rules. STV is
OL,10,Fsponsored, depending on the break, by
OL,11,FSpecSavers and Sun Bingo. It looks
OL,12,Fnaff.
OL,14,FThere is a legitimate debate to be had
OL,15,Faround STV's news proposals.
OL,17,FAudiences are falling.
